## Boundary

This trace validates the current in-process BlogAI consumer boundary only.

BlogAI consumes the boundary through IBlogAiAuthConsumerService.
BlogAiAuthConsumerService remains the local/dev-only implementation.
AdventuresAuthDecisionService remains the auth decision authority.

No web host or middleware was created.
No production deployment was used.
No persistence/database behavior was used.
No OAuth/OpenID behavior was used.
No RBAC, tenant, or organization model was used.
No BlogEngine.NET auth dependency was introduced.

